hopobject.body: Punk not dead can you safely take 800 mg ibuprofen every 4 hours Guha often fails to tease out his subject’s nuances. For example, he notes that the young Gandhi experimented with meat-eating as a way of growing tall, like “the Englishman”, to help in gaining India’s independence. He does not connect this with the later manipulation of diet and fasting that Gandhi considered so essential for the spiritual ascendancy necessary for the independence struggle. Yet it was the same person, same stomach, same political objective. Most nationalists in the 20th century, after all, did not think diet was linked to achieving independence.
